title: Freshmen Preseason All State - Second Team
text:
Freshmen Preseason All State - Second Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
One of the most popular features on Iowa Preps is our preseason All State basketball teams. We take an in-depth look at Class of 2019 and name our second team freshmen All State team. See which of the elite athletes around Iowa made the cut as we take a look towards a winter full of hoops! 
Freshmen Preseason All State - Second Team Sam Allen, Grinnell
